                  <h1>Ferndale, MI: Soulful Yoga with Juliet</h1>
                  <h3>Monday, January 6, 2020 <br> 9:45 AM  10:45 AM</h3>
                  <p>Join Juliet the first Monday of every month for a slow and
                    completely guided yoga practice. In this class we will hold
                    postures for several breaths in order to feel not just the
                    breadth, but also the depth of the asana.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#upcoming-events-carousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
